  "detailed_description": "Trapped and wanting to overthrow the cursed ruler, with a multitude of weapons at your disposal and a fleet of enemies that stop you from progressing, you'll have to fight your way through various terrains to then overthrow the wretched king and claim back what was once yours.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLE STAGES</h2><br>With a multitude of stages, you'll be able to traverse through different areas of the \"Weapons Knight\" world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1652080/extras/b994852057d65a0b4eea8b2b54afe3b2.avif?t=1629473739\" width=600 height=215 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLE WEAPONS</h2><br>With over 10+ weapons at your disposal, you'll be able to quickly cycle through your gallery of weapons and attack foes with what you're given.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1652080/extras/fafca11816cc48b6ae1c5d5e69ee039c.avif?t=1629473739\" width=600 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POWERUPS</h2><br>Weapons Knight comes with a plethora of powerups that will support you through your journey that you can unlock with in-game currency.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1652080/extras/4b3796493c8e7a941ac7a8bee42c61a2.avif?t=1629473739\" width=600 height=96 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADES</h2><br>You'll be able to unlock upgrades to both your gems and how many weapons you have to cycle through, you can purchase these with in-game currency and kills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1652080/extras/e48172ef5f8d94e63bea4a139fd7d31b.avif?t=1629473739\" width=600 height=64 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Trapped and wanting to overthrow the cursed ruler, with a multitude of weapons at your disposal and a fleet of enemies that stop you from progressing, you'll have to fight your way through various terrains to then overthrow the wretched king and claim back what was once yours.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLE STAGES</h2><br>With a multitude of stages, you'll be able to traverse through different areas of the \"Weapons Knight\" world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1652080/extras/b994852057d65a0b4eea8b2b54afe3b2.avif?t=1629473739\" width=600 height=215 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLE WEAPONS</h2><br>With over 10+ weapons at your disposal, you'll be able to quickly cycle through your gallery of weapons and attack foes with what you're given.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1652080/extras/fafca11816cc48b6ae1c5d5e69ee039c.avif?t=1629473739\" width=600 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POWERUPS</h2><br>Weapons Knight comes with a plethora of powerups that will support you through your journey that you can unlock with in-game currency.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1652080/extras/4b3796493c8e7a941ac7a8bee42c61a2.avif?t=1629473739\" width=600 height=96 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADES</h2><br>You'll be able to unlock upgrades to both your gems and how many weapons you have to cycle through, you can purchase these with in-game currency and kills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1652080/extras/e48172ef5f8d94e63bea4a139fd7d31b.avif?t=1629473739\" width=600 height=64 /></span>",
